Euro Advances on Speculation ECB Will Indicate Readiness for Rate Increase

-- B y   N i c h o l a s   R e y n o l d s
-- 
2011-03-01T00:39:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-01/euro-advances-on-speculation-ecb-will-indicate-readiness-for-rate-increase.html
The euro rose against the yen and
the dollar on speculation European Central Bank policy makers
will signal their readiness to raise interest rates to counter
inflation.  The single currency climbed to 113.26 yen as of 9:37 a.m.
in Tokyo from 112.91 yen yesterday in  New York . The euro gained
0.2 percent to $1.3827.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nicholas Reynolds at 
 nreynolds2@bloomberg.net  